public static final class SocialContract.CommunityActivity
extends java.lang.Object
implements SocialContract.DBColumns, SocialContract.SyncColumns, SocialContract.BaseSyncColumns, SocialContract.RecommendationColumns

Represents a table containing all the activities that are added to the activity feeds for communities. You can search the table using a specific community's global ID as feed owner ID.

Author:
